    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some paint thinning on the roof, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and aging suspension components. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics and is comfortable with some upcoming maintenance.",
